Liwa Hotel located 230 kilometers from the City of Abu Dhabi in the midst of beautiful oasis of Liwa Mezairah and Mirfa Hotel located 160 kilometers from the Capital City on the pristine Western Coast of the Emirates are looking for a Garden Supervisor.
The ideal candidate should have ample knowledge and experience on landscaping and prefeably should posses a valid UAE Driving License.The successful candidate should be prepared to supervise other landscaping locations in Abu Dhabi that belongs to the company upon request.
